          "text": "（姚夫人、姚刚、姚能同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫君正朝堂，使我乐安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚能",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文韬武略广，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "力大逞刚强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚能、姚刚",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚能、姚刚",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢母亲！父亲今日上关，这般时候，还不见回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想你父镇守草桥，那得一时安闲？坐在一旁，听为娘道来："
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但愿得四下里狼烟扫尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一家人回朝转乐享安宁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷回府！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚期上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "马、杜、岑奉王命草桥来镇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "调老夫回朝转侍奉当今。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷！王爷今日下关，为何甚迟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人那里知道！今有圣上思念功臣，圣旨到来，调老夫进京，陪王伴驾。草桥"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之事，付与马、杜、岑三位执掌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我主乃有道明君！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人那里知道！今有郭荣在朝专权，有道是："
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伴君如伴虎，昼夜不安宁。一朝龙颜怒，四体不周全！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，爹爹！俺父子镇守边塞，有十大汗马功劳，怕那奸贼何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽！夫人你看姚刚性情倔强，力大无比，此番进京，夫人要严紧教训！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想二子自有妾身照管，王爷不必过虑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！姚刚、姚能打点行李，随为父明日起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚、姚能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "交付兵权印，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚夫人、姚刚、姚能",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回朝见明君。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
