    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "姚刚",
        "姚期",
        "姚能",
        "岑彭",
        "杜茂",
        "马武"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马武、杜茂、岑彭、四龙套同上。姚期、姚刚、姚能、四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，三位皇兄，俺姚期有何德能，怎敢劳动众位皇兄，长亭饯行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武、杜茂、岑彭",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚皇兄，你我亦非一日之交，何出此言！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚刚、姚能，见过你三位叔父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚、姚能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚、姚能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见三位叔父！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武、杜茂、岑彭",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。此二位是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两个犬子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武、杜茂、岑彭",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是少王爷，日后必是皇家栋梁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夸奖了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来来，看酒！姚皇兄，待俺老马把敬你三大杯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讨饶了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众皇兄赐我的饯行酒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大家同饮太平瓯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "回朝参王在那五凤楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚期、姚刚、姚能、四龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，将姚字旗号砍倒，换上马、杜、岑旗号。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜茂、岑彭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！倘若柳蛮反上，何人抵挡？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位皇兄，那柳蛮不来便罢；倘若来时，你我三马连环，出得城去，杀他个落"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花流水！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜茂、岑彭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！众将官，好好把守！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同允。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
